name: After Hours
description:
It was late, Tina waiting for Joyo to closed their records stall, She was hungry, she always hungry during this hour... 

This is the first months they opened a records stall. Tina and Joyo onced worked for a printing company. Tina just resign last week and now she want to follow her dreams to owned a books & record shop. So, this is her new beginning. 

It's getting late and colder, she listens to her favorite playlist while waiting for her partner to get back from the mini market near by, she can't wait to eat those warm and soupy instant noodles.
___
00:17 secs animated drawings with mixed soundcape audio.
